== 相關模板 ==
{{Navbar-header|List of subst helper templates|List of subst helper templates}}
* {{tl|require subst}}: Prints an error unless substituted.
** {{tl|subst check top}}, {{tl|subst check bottom}}: Same purpose, but used as a pair.
** {{tl|subst only}}: For the doc of the above templates; prints a message asking for it be substituted.
** {{tl|nosubst}}: The reverse of {{tl|subst only}}. For the doc of templates which should ''not'' be substituted; prints a message asking for it not to be substituted.
** {{tl|substitution}}: Allows free-fill description of whether the template should be substituted and under what conditions.
* {{tl|issubst}}: Returns "yes" if substituted.
* {{tl|ifsubst}}: Forks if substituted or not.
